The paper discusses the use of automatic audiovisual analysis to enhance metadata information and semantic search for scientific and educational video content. This involves linking the metadata to the Integrated Authority File (GND) of the German National Library, which is a form of linked open data. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Multimedia (cs.MM), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
